        'The creature resembles a large yellow hare with a long (1쩍\'-2\') black horn protruding forwards from the center of its forehead, resembling that of a <a href="/creatures/unicorn">unicorn</a>. In melee it will stab with its horn, its nimbleness giving the horn damage potential of a dagger (1-4 hit points of damage).\n\n'
